description: European diplomats gather with Svetlana Alexievich after she says masked men tried to enter her home.
title: Belarus: Nobel Laureate Alexievich visited by diplomats amid 'harassment'
title_page: Belarus: Nobel Laureate Alexievich visited by diplomats amid 'harassment' - BBC News
maintext: Ms Alexievich, a Nobel Prize-winning writer and journalist, said she had asked supporters to come to her home after she was harassed with door knocks and phone calls. She said masked men had earlier attempted to break into her apartment.
